Class Product

java.lang.Object
  com.mattwilliamsnyc.service.remix.Entity
      com.mattwilliamsnyc.service.remix.Product

public class Product
extends Entity

Representation of a Best Buy catalog product. Note that not all fields are populated on every response. Be sure to check for null values, especially for lists, or complex child elements.
